            "author_info": {
                "name": "Jeffrin Turner",
                "href": "/profile/Jeffrin-Turner"
            },
            "answer_text": " Nobody is a professor in the subject of love. However, trying to express the love for someone is not the easiest thing to do. Professing your love to the special one massively re-affirms the love for them. Words are certainly the most powerful and impactful tool to express or confess what you feel. Most of the people are not very confident while telling their feelings vocally to the one you love. That brings nervousness and awkwardness at times. However, the problem is that almost not everyone is so good with words that they can write efficiently to their loved ones. An effective way to express to express your love to your man is to write a love letter to him. Even if your man is not sensitive enough, it will still be very impactful for him. In order to leave him with tears of joy, you should surely try to write a love letter to him. Not only will it take your relationship to the next level, but it will also show him how much he really means to you. Trust me here, a small piece of paper is capable of showing the emotions that you vocally cannot do. If you will write a love letter to your man, your connection with them will deepen and moreover, he can cherish that memory for life. He can read it whenever he wants to. It will probably decrease the chances of a fight between you both. In bonus, you will get a burst of love which is absolutely worth it. #1. Ignore The Judgement Of Everyone Else And Yourself As an editor of yourself, keep writing even if you feel like tearing your love letter. You might criticize yourself, however, do not let yourself stop because of that. If you will listen to your cracky old brain, you will never be able to write something beautiful for your man. Listen to your pumped and unbiased soul for once and start writing without considering people\u2019s or your own perception for that matter. You need to ignore the professional writer within you and write whatever makes you think of him.  #2. Blend The Ingredients Of Love And Honesty Now it should be understood without even saying. Love letters are not like flowers or puppies. You need to be honest and express your love. Ladies, if you want that after reading your love letter, your man is filled with smiles, love, laughter and what not, tell them everything honestly. Your doubts, your concerns, your feelings, your dark thoughts, your fantasies and even your deepest secrets. You might not believe it before witnessing it that \u2018Love letters are life changing or relationship changing to be very precise. Pour all your heart and soul and don\u2019t worry, if you have been honest enough to do that, it will be certainly visible in the love letter.  read more : How to write Love Letters to your Man? ",
