            "answer_text": "Here\u2019s one I wrote years ago. Dear \"Tom\" I love you. I think I love you. In fact, I'm sure I love you. I love you so much that it hurts me. And I'm terrified to tell you. I'm terrified you will tell me you like me only as a friend. I'm terrified that the boundaries between us will destroy us. You make me smile. You talk to me, so lovingly and gently, you encourage me. You make me feel beautiful and special You are kind and patient. You are funny. You are good natured. You always know how to speak to me. You care about me. I don't even know if I deserve you. But I want to be good enough for you. Maybe you think I'm just doing this to rebel against my parents. I\u2019m not, but...I want to know what you think. Love, Your sweet friend ",
